This paper deals with image-based gender recognition and age estimation using deep neural networks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of transfer learning and pretrained models also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves working with multimedia data (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) in terms of accurately classifying and predicting age based on images.
